snippet.title: Shall we date?: My Fairy Tale+ ~ Gretel ~ Chapter 1
snippet.description:
A very interesting route in my opinion. n_n

A new character in My Fairy Tale was released.
A shy and stubborn artist?
Gretel is added!!
A little stubborn? Gretel is now available!
He is shy, but is very reliable. 
How will you fall in love with him?

If you have any route's requests you can make it and I'll see if it is within my possibilities to do it. 
See you next time!

My invite ID: LcayBNmGDk

I do not own anything within this video, all rights belong to NTT Solmare and others. Please respect their copyrights.

Shall We Date? : My Fairy Tale+ by NTT Solmare

Playlist (music):
